comment: Innaiku Selvi hotel nallave illanu solrala futurela BEKKU BAAKIYALAKSHMI antha hotela superah akkum.  Udane Selvi matrum ellarum Bekku Baakiyalakshmi supera hotela akkittanu solla poranga.  Parunga vennumna.  Bekku Baakiyalakshmi adviseah koduthutte irruku.  Intha munjiya innum ethanai varusham parkanumo, kadavulukuthan velicham.  Intha seriala like panniyelam parkala but to see how Bekku is going to do again.  Inthama ellarum thittu vanga appuram ellarum paratuvanga.  Intha loosuku vera velaiye illa.     Kudumbame loosunga.
